## ðŸ”„ Data Pipeline Flow

1. Raw datasets uploaded (People + Companies)
2. Cleaning pipelines remove duplicates, standardize fields, and generate keys
3. Cleaned datasets power ontology objects
4. Employment object links PERSON and COMPANY
5. Dashboard visualizes CRM relationships

